    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed status consistent with MRL 2 assessment plan. Hemolysis index predictions are within acceptable validation uncertainty bounds across the CPB operating envelope. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the Class II CPB device context as described in the Claim and Requirement documentation.",
